active_record_random_find
=========================

Inspired by http://weblog.jamisbuck.org/2006/10/7/helping-activerecord-finders-help-you

How to find a random model in the database using ActiveRecord

Step 1: In your rails root, do this:

./script/plugin install git://github.com/mshiltonj/active_record_random_find

Step 2: Starting finding random models:

winnner = User.find :random

Step 3:

PROFIT!!!!!!!


